        <p style="font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);line-height:1.55;padding-left:22px">{entry.desc}</p>
        <span style="font-size:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);padding-left:22px;display:block;margin-top:3px">{entry.date}</span>
      </div>
    ))}
